      1          /**
      2           *  @file       
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      SR Reading and Filtering of an I2C Pressure Sensor
      5           *
      6           *  @details    Interacts with the I2C driver to request and read Pressures sensor data.
      7           *              This Module Runs an IIR Filter on the Incoming data. Returns a known invalid value while the filter settles.
      8           *              If the I2C data request is not received within a configured time a fault is set.
      9           *
     10           *  @defgroup   CLASS_B
     11           *
     12           *  @copyright  Copyright 2018. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     13           */
